data.description: Looking for peace and privacy? Look No further! This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home nestled on a spacious 3-acre lot. With over 1500 sqft of living space, this residence is a haven of privacy that you'll truly appreciate. The living room is bathed in natural light and features a cozy wood-burning fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Recent upgrades include a new HVAC unit and water heater, ensuring modern comfort. Situated in the desirable Eclectic School zone, this home is ready for its new owners to make lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make this peaceful retreat your own—schedule a viewing today before it's too late!
